e 係跟機）<br />\n- Windows Key Licence 好似跟底板<br />\n<br />\n- 如果我洗左機 reset哂所有野 裝埋防毒 但佢有我Ip 同 實體地址 佢會有可能攻擊入到黎？<br />\n- 裝埋 Windows Update Patch 就難d攻入<br />\n<br />\n- 咁驚既話，裝Linux 啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 用緊windows 10</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明啵 唔係IT佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠一打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f45f00c9d0e18186f610ec205ba19c64569275","tid":309003,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔使洗兩次咩洗底板啊<br />\n你裝返同一隻硬碟，揀format再裝，乜都清哂啦，當然backup咗檔案資料先<br />\n你想順便換隻SSD另作別論"},{"pid":"07c3208bc54c27928d19c7c464195ea5d0571ca3","tid":309003,"uid":21014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw洗機原來唔係無敵架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前試過中左過勁野都係洗機搞掂 冇諗過洗完佢仲可以攻擊你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係嫁<br />\n之前我research過 <br />\n佢木馬可以入到底板（display 唔知得唔得）<br />\n仲可以記底你網卡 電腦個實體地址搵你出黎 （如果佢有心搞你）<br />\n你可以做ge野就係轉